title: 'Grey's Anatomy' Star Camilla Luddington Spoofs Beyonce, Reveals If She's Having a Baby Boy or Girl

Camilla Luddington is currently pregnant with her first child and she just revealed the happy news that she’s having a baby girl! 
The 33-year-old Grey’s Anatomy actress is currently expecting with her boyfriend Matthew Alan .
